												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[GERRY] The player turns and faces Mizora. She is naked, her wings spreads her wings wide., , The flame circle kicks up higher, the player and Mizora float off of the ground., , Mizora looks deeply into the player's eyes and pulls their hands to her breasts."
												}
