													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The player turns and faces Mizora. She is naked, her wings spreads her wings wide.\r\n\r\nThe flame circle kicks up higher, the player and Mizora float off of the ground.\r\n\r\nJLatino: \"Mizora looks deeply into the player's eyes and pulls their hands to her breasts.\" Can we do the Into Wing beat without this, will that save anything?"
