													"value": "The player's flame glows deep blue for a moment, then glows back to bright red at the end of the line.\r\n\r\nThe player extends both arms out toward the flames, palms down. Their eyes close as they connect with Mizora's hellish offerings.\r\n\r\nShe watches as the pleasure rides out the sensations."
