												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The player reaches out to the flames, hesitently letting them dance around their fingers. Then they cup their hand bringing some of the flame back, close to their chest.\r\n\r\nThe player makes a fist, the flame extinguishes, but in doing so a new flood of sensation rushes into their core. Their back and neck arch slightly as they breath deep."
												}
