												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[GERRY] The flame wall shifts color to red and necrotic black., , The shape of Mizora cocooning the player in her wings is sillouetted against the blazing backdrop., , The player struggles, but does not break free of the wings. Whatever can be seen of their feet moving is the limited testiment of whether they are alive or dead., , N21"
