													"value": "The flame wall shifts color to red and necrotic black.\r\n\r\nThe shape of Mizora cocooning the player in her wings is sillouetted against the blazing backdrop.\r\n\r\nThe player struggles, but does not break free of the wings. Whatever can be seen of their feet moving is the limited testiment of whether they are alive or dead."
												}
